transcript:
[Ringing]
Executive: Hello
Customer: Hello
Executive: Haan good afternoon sir meri baat KCS power mein ho rahi hai.
Customer: Haan KCS power se baat ho rahi hai.
Executive: Ji ji ji main Ashraf baat kar raha hun sir India mart ke head office se kaise hain aap.
Customer: Haan haan.
Executive: Ji ji ji wo kuch kuch changes karane the na sir aapko apne website pe.
Customer: Aur haan wo to hai main suniye na suniye na main thoda bahar aaya hun ek ghante ke baad call karta hun theek hai na.
Executive: Theek hai ek ghante baad fir main aapko karta hun baki yahi bas yahi changes hi to karane hain sir aapko apne website mein humse aur koi issue hai.
Customer: Nahi nahi changes nahi nahi bahut sara issue hai thoda main bahar hun main.
Executive: Achcha chaliye theek hai tab fir karta hun main aapko ek ghante baad.
Customer: Theek hai theek hai theek hai thank you thank you.
summary:
Concerns:

- Wants changes on the website.

- Has many issues.



Resolution:

- Executive agreed to call after one hour.



Next Steps: 

- Issue not resolved. Executive will call in one hour.



Alert (If Any):

None

@@@Sentiment:

- Neutral -> Neutral



@@@Key Topics:
